"{\"notes\":[{\"Author\":\"karen_davis\",\"Date\":\"Apr 6, 2016 9:23:35 PM\",\"Note\":\"L'illustrazione di primo piano non occupa interamente il quadro.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato non occupa tutto il quadro. Devi inviare un'illustrazione di primo piano che occupi interamente il quadro.

Illustrazione con l'ultimo template di iTunes Connect necessaria.
Invia di nuovo l'illustrazione a iTunes Connect usando l'ultimo template di primo piano 4320 x 1080.

La grafica del titolo all'interno del file deve essere localizzata.
Il livello della grafica del titolo all'interno dell'illustrazione contiene solo una localizzazione. Nella grafica del titolo devi includere tutte le localizzazioni del nome dell'app applicabili. Nel file, tutte le localizzazioni del nome dell'app devono trovarsi su livelli separati. In questo modo, il team di progettazione dell'App Store avrà più flessibilità con l'illustrazione promozionale, nel caso in cui la tua app dovesse essere scelta per una promozione sull'App Store.

Lo Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV richiede un'illustrazione a contrasto più basso.
Modifica la tua risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV. Tutti i contenuti a sinistra dell'area di visualizzazione sicura in verde dovrebbero essere a basso contrasto. Al momento, la tua illustrazione è in conflitto con l'interfaccia utente.

Nell'illustrazione di primo piano manca la grafica del titolo.
Nel file dell'illustrazione di primo piano manca il titolo. Devi inviare l'illustrazione grafica del titolo su un livello separato. Inoltre, deve poter essere rimpicciolita o ingrandita, come un livello \"Oggetti avanzati\" di Photoshop.

Rimuovi il testo dalla risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV.
Rimuovi eventuale testo dalla risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV.

Rimuovi il logo dalla risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV.
Modifica la risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV per rimuovere il logo dal file PNG. Il logo Apple TV inviato verrà sovrapposto automaticamente.

L'illustrazione di primo piano ha un tag o byline sul livello del titolo.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato contiene tag o byline sullo stesso livello del titolo. Devi rimuovere i tag o le byline dal livello attuale o posizionarli su un livello separato. Inoltre, l'illustrazione di primo piano deve poter essere rimpicciolita o ingrandita, come un livello \"Oggetti avanzati\" di Photoshop.

L'illustrazione di primo piano non contiene una grafica del titolo o un logo.
Devi inviare un'illustrazione che faccia uso di tutto il modello, che contenga un titolo o un logo su un livello separato e che possa essere rimpicciolita o ingrandita, come in un livello \"Oggetti avanzati\" di Photoshop.

Le risorse TV sono necessarie.
Fornisci lo Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV e il Logo a tutto schermo per TV.

Elementi esterni all'area sicura nello Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV.
Modifica la risorsa Sfondo a tutto schermo per TV per rimuovere gli elementi che si trovano all'esterno dell'area di visualizzazione sicura in verde.

L'illustrazione di primo piano contiene temi destinati a un pubblico adulto.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato contiene immagini e temi violenti o destinati a un pubblico adulto, non adatti all'App Store. L'illustrazione di primo piano non può avere contenuti raffiguranti sesso, violenza, spargimento di sangue, sostanze stupefacenti, linguaggio esplicito o istigazione all'odio.

L'illustrazione di primo piano contiene immagini di dispositivi Apple.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato contiene rappresentazioni visive di un dispositivo Apple. L'illustrazione di primo piano deve rispecchiare le qualità e le caratteristiche della tua app e non può contenere rappresentazioni visive di dispositivi Apple.

L'illustrazione di primo piano contiene pistole puntate verso personaggi o utenti.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato contiene pistole puntate verso altri personaggi o verso l'utente. L'illustrazione di primo piano non può contenere immagini non appropriate per l'App Store.

Immagine di sfondo con più elementi sullo stesso livello.
L'immagine di sfondo che hai inviato ha più elementi sullo stesso livello. Devi riformattare l'immagine in modo che ciascun elemento si trovi su un livello separato. In questo modo il team di progettazione dell'App Store avrà più flessibilità con la tua copertina promozionale nel caso in cui la tua app dovesse essere selezionata per una promozione sull'App Store.

L'illustrazione di primo piano è ritagliata male.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato ha un design che contiene personaggi, oggetti o foto troncati. Nelle immagini, evita di troncare i visi o altre parti del corpo. Invia un'illustrazione di primo piano con un'immagine che non sia troncata o coperta.

La grafica del titolo richiede una risoluzione maggiore.
L'illustrazione grafica del titolo manca o non è scalabile. Le illustrazioni grafiche del titolo all'interno del file devono essere disposte su un livello separato e devono poter essere rimpicciolite o ingrandite, come un livello \"Oggetti avanzati\" di Photoshop.

Nuovo concetto del design.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato non offre una rappresentazione adeguata della tua app. Invia un'altra illustrazione con un nuovo concetto del design.

L'illustrazione di primo piano non descrive l'app.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato non descrive la tua app, le sue qualità o caratteristiche. L'illustrazione deve riguardare la tua app e deve rispecchiarne in modo realistico le caratteristiche.

L'illustrazione di primo piano è pixelata.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato è pixelata. Invia un'illustrazione con una risoluzione maggiore e che non sia pixelata, soprattutto per quanto riguarda il titolo.

Protagonista collocato all'esterno dell'area di visualizzazione sicura in verde.
Devi includere tutti i protagonisti, i volti, le grafiche del titolo e i personaggi all'interno dell'area di visualizzazione sicura in giallo, per garantire che i contenuti vengano ritagliati correttamente su tutti i dispositivi supportati.

La grafica del titolo contiene l'icona dell'app.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato contiene l'icona dell'app nella grafica del titolo.

L'illustrazione di primo piano contiene marchi registrati nel design.
L'illustrazione di primo piano che hai inviato potrebbe contenere design che sono marchi registrati di terze parti. Se non disponi dei diritti per utilizzare questi materiali, fornisci un file alternativo senza i marchi commerciali. Rows.descript:
*DV: I can't test the app, as the code never shows up after inputting my phone number*

New App / L:EN / Upshot is a new camera app focused on social events. Leveraging Interactive notifications & 3D Touch, Upshot lets you autoshare your camera roll for a specific event and group for the duration of the event. Super clear and easy sharing / privacy controls. Great solution to a common problem.

Rows.descript: New Game // L: EN, FR, DE, RU // Punch Club is a strategy / tycoon / streetfighter-manager game with 80-90s atmosphere, nostalgia and lots of games/movies references. You have to manage your time and money to improve your fighter skills on one side and your training equipment on the other. You will start as an unknown fighter in the underground club and must work your way to the top and solve the mystery from your past. The game is a mix of a non-linear storyline, a tycoon-like gameplay, RPG elements and a tactical fight. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=345g7VNvnOo

Rows.contentTitle: Tasteful - Vegetarian, Vegan, Gluten-Free, Paleo Restaurants and Dishes
Rows.descript:
LB Updates: 
1. Force touch gesture implementation for Restaurant objects everywhere.
2. Force touch Dynamic menu for users for easy access to restaurants
3. Integrated restaurant search results with Spotlight search.
4. Simplified and much improved Shout out flow for users to express their like/dislike of restaurants and dishes
5. Improved On-boarding flow.
6. Improved recommendations tab "For you", by removing activity and also adding special restaurant collections ordered by Location, Time, mood.
7. Moved Activity to its own Tab to help users discover restaurants via activity 
8. Added easy access to Search on For you tab.
9. Improved Map Zoom level when user goes to Nearby or searches for restaurants.
10. Bug fixes.

Rows.descript: UPDATED App: My Jump calculates the jump height using the camera on the iPhone or iPad / L: EN, CN, FR, DE, IT, JP, ES / UPDATE 3.0 version adds Search - Core Spotlight: Access to the users defined in My Jump by entering their names in Spotlight. quickly view their best and last jumps. 3D Touch Home screen quick actions: Shortcuts to open the most recent video, record a new video, and see user list. Jump Type: Possibility to order the jump in 4 different categories: Countermovement Jump, Squat Jump, Drop Jump and Countermovement Jump free arms. Drop Jump: Box Height parameter specific to Drop Jumps (instead of the load parameter). Edit jump: Possibility to edit a jump result to change the associated user, the jump type and other parameters // DRI: Cyrille

7. 从现在起，您可以在名片夹输入任何企业名称，查询该企业信用信息
8. 支持将“企业信息页”分享到微信" / DRI: Chi

Rows.descript:
*LL: Add to 3D Touch collection*We are particularly excited about the support for 3D Touch on iPhone 6s and 6s Plus in this release. We added a number of Quick Actions to the Springboard icon (New Item, Favorites, and Search) as well as full peek n’ pop support within the app for all of our item lists. With both of these new features in place we’ve drastically sped up a very common 1Password workflow: To find and copy a password out of 1Password you can now 3D touch on the app icon, select Search, Touch ID to unlock, perform your search, peek the item you want and then swipe up to copy the item’s password from the actions menu. It’s really, really cool.

On top of that we’ve completely rewritten our internal search functionality to be blazingly fast, added support for 1Password Watchtower (which notifies you if a site has been compromised), added the ability to copy and move items to different vaults, and added a whole bunch of support for 1Password for Teams.

Rows.descript:
*LL: Add to 3D Touch collection* 
UPDATE: Home is a home automation app for iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch to control and manage HomeKit compatible accessories. Users can create homes, rooms, zones, scenes and triggers.

This update adds support for 3D Touch – e.g. users to execute scenes using Quick Actions. Also the support for triggers is improved to allow more complex event triggers.

iOS Technologies supported: 3D Touch, iPad Split View, Handoff, HomeKit

Rows.descript:
tvOS version + Updates

"[UPDATE]

Pogo Chick in now available on Apple TV!!

We took a lot of care to refine this version and adapt the controls for the perfect couch experience.

We also made the game MUCH SIMPLER in process. The result is astonishing given the playtest sessions we conducted. People loved it so much that we included this change in the iOS version as well.

The game now feels much more dynamic and the difficulty has been shifted from hard controls to challenging procedural terrains, for a much more rewarding experience.

This is the ultimate version of the game: on iOS and tvOS. The little bird is finally ready to take off!"

Rows.descript:
L: E,F,I,G,S, J,K,C, B,R,T, ID

iOS update + tvOS version


Update: "PVP MODE 
* New PvP Map - Pagoda Peaks Night - The ultimate test of your PvP skills as you hunt for your opponent in the darkness of night! 
* Victory Taunts - show off your winning moves with a victory taunt after PvP combat. Select from 7 different taunts - Fist Pump, Grand Slam, Shoulder Dust, Bow, Salute and more! 
* Promotion Challenges - quickly rise up the PvP ranks by beating intensive challenges and earning rewards! 

The Whiteout Global Ops Event is coming! 
* New Global Ops Map - battle amid the remnants of Anubis' base in the icy, far north for leaderboard domination! 
* New Global Ops Missions - crafted exclusively for the Whiteout Global Ops event! 

Alliance Enhancements! 
* Alliance Mail - send messages directly to your alliance members to better coordinate your activities! 
* Alliance Emblems - collect, customize, and equip new emblems to represent your alliance! "

Rows.descript:
NEW tvOS App // The popular social racing game for iOS comes to Apple TV! USP's: split screen play, multi player mode supporting 3rd party controllers. Unlock all tracks with a single IAP. // DRI: Renate Nyborg

- Core Game: the same as the single player game (with some features removed for various reasons - see list below), with the same FTUE and monetisation features.
- A new split-screen multi-player mode for Apple TV: Players can race each other on the TV in a split-screen mode. Players can use the Apple TV Remote plus a third party remote, or they can use two third party remotes.
- A new iAP: that unlocks all the tracks and one kart for each track. This is to enable someone who is interested in the multiplayer to be able to quickly unlock all the tracks.
- Features removed from the Apple TV version: Jenga, Team-based Multiplayer, Local Multiplayer (i.e. one player on the Apple TV and one playing on their iDevice screen), Facebook (as no web connection), Like buttons (as no web connection), Toons (as no web connection), Ads (as no web connection), iTunes purchase soundtrack (as no web connection).
- General specifications:
UI/UX optimised for Apple TV controller
HDR rendering
Improved Texture detail for the majority of game assets (original ones were scaled down)
60 FPS (also for 2 player split screen) (target frame rate)
More VFX particles and shader improvement

Rows.contentTitle: CatHotel - Care for cute cats, cuddle them and play with them
Rows.descript:
New Game // L: EN, DE, FR, ES, IT, JP, RU, UK, KO, BR-PT, PT-PT,  CN // "THE FEATURES AT A GLANCE

# Manage your own cat hotel
# Develop your cattery from a small hotel into a 5-star luxury accommodation for the little sweeties
# From the trusting Maine Coon to the graceful Burma – care for and feed six different breeds of cats
# Decorate and design your cat hotel with individual objects
# Play with your cats using the cat teaser toy, motivate them with the laser pointer game or groom their fur with different brushes
"

Rows.descript: New Game // L: EN, FR, IT, DE, ES, DA, PT, NL  // Ride, Build, Share and Compete! Experience the heart-pounding and adrenaline-packed thrills of Downhill, Freeride and Slopestyle mountain biking. Beat Pro Riders, trail challenges, conquer mountains, build trails, upgrading bikes & components and compete against friends. Built from the ground up for iOS as the ultimate touch-based extreme sports game. Mountain Biker’s features include: Simple & intuitive finger controls. Build trails with drag-and-drop. Heavily integrated into Game Centre. Beat 14 Pro Riders. 18 Authentic Bikes from 6 Brands. 50+ componenents from 7 component manufacturers. 18 Tricks to learn. 3 great locations to conquer. Seamless Online & Offline Game-Play! // iOS Exclusive

Rows.descript: New Game // L: FR only // The 12 Hits of Mid-day ("Les 12 coups de Midi") is a very famous TV show in France. It's being  followed on TV every day by 3.5 millions people. On the webgame, there's more than 3 million people playing.

Rows.contentTitle: Carousell - Snap to Sell, Chat to Buy
Rows.descript:
HK and Australia launch: it’s been over 3 years since Carousell first launched as one of the first apps in the mobile marketplace space - and the first in Singapore. They have over 26 million listings and 8 million successful transactions across countries such as Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia and Taiwan. After soft-launching these past few months, they are planning to finally launch in Hong Kong and Australia in January 2016 and turn up user acquisition activities by a few notches.

New Group features: In order to connect users to encourage more conversations, they've developed a new featured called "Carousell Groups", for Carousellers to buy and sell with friends, people of similar interests, and communities that they care about. If you’re interested in Handmade Craft, join our Handmade Group to connect with fellow crafters. If you are a fan of brands like Forever 21 or Kate Spade, join these Groups to connect on old trends and discover the new.

Rows.descript: *MH: Available WW, EN-only, USA content only. 2.0 update went live in December but now is a great time to feature apps to help you get in shape. This particular app focuses on US national parks and goes into great detail on about 6-8 of them and minor detail on another 20. They tell you info about when the parks are open, camping options, food & drink nearby, gems you should lookout for, and featured hikes. All in all, a very polished app and it's all for free.*

Rows.contentTitle: Easy Music - give kids an ear for music
Rows.descript:
NEW App / L:  EN, FR, ES, PT, DE, IT, EL, NL, FI, NO, SV, DA, TR,RU, KO, ID, MS, VI, JP, TH, ZH (Traditional), ZH (Simplified)  / NEW: "Give kids an ear for music"

Easy Music is the perfect initiation into the world of music, no theory required! It is a beautifully animated app to introduce kids aged 3+ to musicality.

The app launches simultaneously on iOS/tvOS and comes with a super fun watchOS app that allows parents to jam with their kids by controlling an in-app drum from their wrist!

Children learn to recognize notes, pitch, rhythm, and melody in a nature-inspired game environment. An interactive sand castle serves as a musical playground where curious kids can experiment with various instruments, genres of music and objects freely to compose their first music piece. // DRI: Renate

Next Numbers 2 is a follow up to the highly successful NN1.
It's a brain game that trains concentration, reaction speed, and attention. Tap by tap, travel through a spooky night in a desert, ghost islands, sky village, and a desolate road where the dragon lives. Challenge your friends on Facebook and beat their score. Special Xmas edition suggests a level with holiday music, attributes. The game lets the Xmas miracle begin.
This app was tested and highly recommended by Munich, Berlin and Hamburg clinics as nice training app against Absent-mindedness.

Rows.contentTitle: Basic Math Skills for School with Numbie. Learning games for Kindergarten, Preschool and First Grade kids.
Rows.descript:
Global release of great math educational game for kids from Plarium. 
Based on Editorial team feedback, developer implemented the following changes during soft launch to be ready for global release. 
Unique style. We will bring our unique style forward in the coming update.   
 
Our "selling point".
Numbie is a game-based educational app using proven methodology with a year’s worth of content fully narrated into 10 languages.
Numbie offers:
Complete coverage of First Grade Curriculum;
Over 1400 games resulting in exceptionally high rolling retention levels with over 70% of users returning monthly and 27% yearly;
It is professionally designed, animated and fully narrated into 10 languages.

Complexity level too low in the beginning. We will address this to progress quicker, where the first few levels will even out the math skills and move from there to First Grade math. The first chapter will be dynamic and intense on storytelling.

On top of that, we will offer users who subscribe to Numbie to go straight to the desired level of complexity.

Adaptive gameplay. Plarium Education recognizes the direction educational apps are going towards, with that, Numbie was designed to offer children exploration and experimentation with math. We would like our users to explore Numbie by advancing along the levels, but we also encourage children to go back and play levels they enjoy repeatedly (just as they read a book or watch a movie they enjoy repeatedly), even if that level may be considered “too easy”. We would like Numbie to be considered a math playground, rather than a form of assessment. As educators we recognize that children often need repetition, they need to have a sense of control, as well as familiarity, which all add to their feelings of confidence, efficacy and their ability to learn math! 

Solving by guessing. We are aware that Numbie included a few levels in which a child may proceed through guessing, or trial and error. “Digital Native” children often approach new content through trial and error. Indeed, by offering this option we are encouraging learners to explore and try. Furthermore, It is very important according to our educational philosophy, not to frustrate our learners. There were instances in which the user experience, the flow, the need to remain intuitive, and our desire to provide learners with experiences of success, that dictated this need. 
With that, all of Numbie’s math concepts are reintroduced spirally throughout the app that progressively bring our learners to higher order thinking skills which cannot be achieved through guessing or trial and error. 

The “?” tutorial to each card. One of the greatest difficulties to overcome in math education is the child’s feeling of inability.  Many children develop a sense that they are not capable of learning math, that they are a failure at math, that math is too hard for them and they will never be good at it. These are the feelings that Numbie does not want to instill in any child. Our entire development process is based on providing the right balance between fun, exploration and challenge so that no child will feel frustrated with math. In Numbie one does not set out to get a high score, or to complete a level in limited amount of time. We intentionally want our users to enjoy what they are doing, and to come back and do the level again and again.  Our “Help” option is available to show users what they need to do when they have a difficulty.  Children who use the help in one card do not need it in subsequent cards which suggests to us that they have learned how to solve the task. Finally, we know that only 3% of users actually ever press the “?” tutorial button, which means almost all of users understand what is required of them and can solve the problem on their own.

"{"notes":[{"Author":"ati.studios@yahoo.com","Date":"Jan 6, 2016 1:14:07 PM","Note":"Hello App Store Team,

Thank you for sending us this invitation and Happy New Year!
We're really excited with such a promising start in 2016.

Regarding the Featuring Art, we've created a simple but expressive design which includes: 
- the app's name and logo 
- the 26 flags which have double meaning as they represent both the languages being taught and the languages from which any language can be learned. We've looked to convey this double meaning by placing the flags on an elliptic path.
- the colour orange-peach found in the app's icon 
- the word "languages" which is separate from the name and can be optional.

I'd like to mention our motto: "Play your way to a new language".

If you need additional information or modifications for this art, our team is ready to reply in the shortest possible time.


Best regards,
Alexandru Iliescu
CEO ATi Studios"}]}"

Rows.descript:
《敢达决战》为中国大陆首款正版授权敢达题材手游，由株式会社万代南梦宫娱乐与DeNA中国合力打造。《机动战士敢达》《机动战士Z敢达》《机动战士敢达SEED》《机动战士敢达UC》等经典人气作品悉数登场。敢达、Z敢达、自由敢达、强袭敢达、独角兽等数十台人气机体全数出击，众多耳熟能详的经典人物阿姆罗?雷、夏亚?阿兹纳布尔、基拉?大和、卡缪?维丹等一同前来助阵，赶紧加入，打造一个属于自己的华丽阵容。

游戏特色：
·百台机体，经典人物悉数登场
·尊重原著，重温经典对话剧情
·超高质感，完美画面精细呈现
·触控释放，策略动作双重乐趣
·激光对射，导弹横飞热血战斗
·宇宙远征，漫漫征途精彩不断
·竞技排名，巅峰荣耀王者降临

全面战争，GUNDAM出击！

Rows.contentTitle: Shoto - Get the Photos your Friends take | Share Pictures with Friends | Private Photo Albums
Rows.descript:
- Album Match gets you the albums where friends have photos and let's you request photos instantly.
- The Library is a beautiful curated timeline of your photos and the photos your friends have shared with you. Instantly searchable and easy to browse.
- New icons on photos tell you if they are private, shared or public.
- "Album Completeness" Progress bar on every Album that has potential for friends to send you photos - so you can see how much of the photos you can see you actually have in hand.

Rows.descript: 1.0/en/new: The Wild Kratts Baby Buddies App needs your help with taking care of a young zebra, elephant, cheetah, crocodile and aardvark! Join Martin, Chris, and the Wild Kratts team on an African Savannah creature sitting adventure. These baby animals need a lot of attention and care, and with Wild Kratts Baby Buddies app, you are in charge of feeding, washing, protecting and playing with each one. The Wild Kratts team will be there with some facts and tips to help you learn the baby animals amazing creature powers along the way.

Rows.descript:
[App Preview] / [L]: EN, FR, DE, IT, ES, CN, CS, PT, RU, JP, KR, AR, TH, BA, AR, TH, TR, ID / Update: "MEGA UPDATE +(iOS + TvOS)
The Adament Alliance update offers to all players an opportunity to discover a whole new co-op mode, the Chinese New Year and to craft their own minions:
- Discover a whole new synchronous CO-OP with up to 4 players!
- Band together with your allies: Create a party or join one at any time!
- Chat with your party while you play to unite your efforts
- Complete weekly quests and Earn Minions
- Earn enough Shards of the same type to craft minions to defend your stronghold
- Chinese New Year: Ring in the new year at the temple of bells during one week special event" / DRI: Nicola/Spiro

Rows.contentTitle: mapstr - keep track of your places, your world
Rows.descript: UPDATED App:Mapstr, map-meets-notes app, lets you save any place you want in the world in just a few seconds / L: EN, FR / APP UPDATE: v1.2.0 Fully revamped design, Apple WatchOS 2 (with support of non reachable iPhone), iOS 9 Spotlight, Dynamic Types with System fonts, Rewritten main code for performance, Add a Time Machine-like feature to recover old data if deleted by mistake // DRI: Cyrille

- 12 cameras including new Pop Gold Square and Pop Splitzer.
- 20 filters including new Drama filter.
- Fix bugs

Rows.descript:
/ [App Preview] / [L]:EN, SP, DE, FR
  /Update: / DRI: Yohei

Major Update (V2.0)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                - New Boss Pit Feature:                                                                                3 New custom designed bosses that each take 3 days to complete with 1 stage available each day.  Beating bosses requires new tactics based on two new systems: Damage Types & Hero Tags.                                                                            - New Bosses Include:                                                                            -     "Venusia - Eater of Heroes", a giant carnivorous plant                    -     "The Golden Beacon, a colossus immune to most attacks                              -     "The Savvy Summoner, a necromancer who summons ghosts                                                                                                                                                            - New Campaign Chapter 12:                                                                         -      Level Cap increase to 85                                                                        -      Access to Purple +4 gear and promotions                                                                                          - 3 New Heroes:                                                                                          -      "Orc Monk",  A healer and buffer                                                                        -      "Rabid Dragon", A crazy dragon that damages over time                                                -      "Dwarven Archer", A backline Sniper                                                               - 2 New Enemies:                                                                                       -      "Cauldron Monster" damages only when you spill his cauldron -      "Squid Squirter" sprays ink & debuffs heroes for entire battle                                                                                                        - New Soul Mart Shop allows players to trade extraneous soulstones for high-level gear.                                                                - New Events & Rewards:                                                                           -      Level Challenge event rewards every time a player levels up during an event                                                                                      -      Special, high-value consumables that can only be earned through events.                                                                                    - Combat Stats Update exposes more combat stats to players & explains how they work in a detailed set of screens                                                                                  - UX Improvements:  tons of UX improvements to help reduce number of clicks to play.

Rows.contentTitle: Microsoft OneNote – lists, photos, and notes, organized in a notebook
Rows.descript:
*Add to 3D Touch Collection*
* We've added notifications to let you know if something interesting happened while you were away
* We spiffied up Search over the holidays and added some new tricks! Now, you can: search all of your OneDrive notebooks, even if they're not on your device; zippier results – so zippy you can search for things you're already reading and *almost* find them quicker; and, as before, view see glimpses of notes you haven't written yet. Wait. Not that last one. But the rest!
* iPad Multitasking is better: Multitask like never before: Side-by-Side and Slideover views now support Searching, Sharing, and viewing the title of your open notebook.

Rows.contentTitle: Uberchord Guitar - Free Chord Trainer That Listens & Adapts to You On The Fly.
Rows.descript:
NEW: Uberchord is an interactive guitar trainer. It uses a patent-pending chord recognition to listen to the player through the built-in microphone. It works with a real guitar and gives instant feedback even for the most complex chords at an unprecedented level. The learning path takes the beginner step by step from their first chords to playing a full song, seamlessly adapting to your personal progress in complexity and speed. In oposite to competitors (e.g. Yousician, JoyTunes) the technology can exactly understand mistakes and help the user to learn from them (the competition can only tell right or wrong). /

iOS exclusive / 

L: EN, DE, FR, ES, PORT, JP, KOR /

Showcase: https://docsend.com/view/acv925m /
